item.title: About_me
item.description: Hello friend Hello and welcome to this highly sophisticated piece of writing (my blog) First ever piece of article requires an introduction. My name is Jacob, I’m 22, I work as a backend python developer. This blog won’t only be about programming and IT related stuff, I’ll try to post from time to time. I’m very curious about few things: Will anyone come across this blog Will I post here after 2 weeks ?
